I know I post a lot of us working. So I figured I’d post this fun video! Dad and I put out minerals all morning and then he surprised me; saying that we could go shopping once we were done. So I figured I’d post this because sometimes the little things mean more than the big things. Even though it might not have been his thing. Since it was something I enjoy he did it anyways. See we always are having fun but sometimes it’s fun to make special quick trips.
